---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | MinBlog" description="Learn more about MinBlog and its author">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        Welcome to MinBlog, a minimalist blog focused on delivering quality content without distractions.
        This blog was created with a design philosophy that prioritizes readability, accessibility, and user experience.
      </p>
      
      <h2>The Author</h2>
      <p>
        [Your introduction here] Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam in dui mauris. 
        Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie vehicula. Sed auctor neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend nibh porttitor.
      </p>
      
      <h2>The Blog</h2>
      <p>
        MinBlog is built with Astro, a modern static site generator that allows for incredible performance while maintaining 
        developer experience. The site features:
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>Responsive design that works well on all devices</li>
        <li>Dark and light theme support</li>
        <li>Markdown-based content for easy writing</li>
        <li>Fast loading times</li>
        <li>SEO optimization</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions or want to reach out? You can contact me through:
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com">your.email@example.com</a></li>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/dmuolhoi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@dmuolhoi</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  ul {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>